  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But suddenly, he got food again because we sold the coat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had-- you know, it was, of course, a little bit of variety.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Whatever there was to be had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And my mother could cook something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the time was when they were telling us that there would be a ghetto soon.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My father had been out for a long time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And for what reason ever, we went to Bochnia, a town not far from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Quite a few miles, but not very far.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say it was '41 already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there we came to a family, and the name only-- at first, when I first wrote my script to my book, I didn't know the name until I found somebody who knew the family only almost recently.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The name is Fogelhut.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, whereas in my German translation I use the name in this book, I don't know if I managed to put it-- found it in time to put it in my English version.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway, Fogelhut.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because-- I name names because in the hope that if anybody reads my book or sees the film, would come across anybody who knows these names.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And perhaps in my lifetime will come back to me and say oh, yes, I know these people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in some cases, we had to be-- have to give my belated thanks for things, and in other cases I could say, well, I have a word to speak with you.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well the Germans sort of, you know, you could-- you could hear very great anti-Semitic incidents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But not actual mass killings of any sort, Hear of atrocities when they caught religious Jews and they cut their beards and other things, what--",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
